#: error_dialogs.py:26
msgid ""
"Can't find Python. Please read the <a href='{}'>document</a> "
"of how to install Python."
msgstr "找不到 Python。請閱讀如何安裝 Python 的<a href='{}'>文件</a>。"

#: error_dialogs.py:36
msgid ""
"Your Python version is too old, please update to a newer version "
"and read the <a href='{}'>document</a> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Python 版本過舊，請更新至較新的版本，並閱讀<a href='{}'>文件</a>以取得更多"
"資訊。"

#: error_dialogs.py:46
msgid ""
"Please install an older version and put the Python binary file "
"path in the plugin's preferences window."
msgstr "請安裝較舊的版本，並在外掛程式的偏好設定視窗中填入 Python 執行檔路徑。"

#: error_dialogs.py:60
msgid ""
"Please use "
"<a href='https://github.com/kevinhendricks/KindleUnpack'>"
"KindleUnpack</a>'s '-s' option to split the book."
msgstr ""
"請使用 <a href='https://github.com/kevinhendricks/"
"KindleUnpack'>KindleUnpack</a> 的「-s」選項來拆分書籍。"

#: error_dialogs.py:71
msgid ""
"Install <a href='https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/2977003/"
"the-latest-supported-visual-c-downloads'>"
"Visual C++ 2019 Redistributable</a>"
msgstr ""
"請安裝 <a href='https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/2977003/"
"the-latest-supported-visual-c-downloads'>"
"Visual C++ 2019 Redistributable</a>"

#: error_dialogs.py:81
msgid "Download failed"
msgstr "下載失敗"

#: error_dialogs.py:82
msgid "Download failed, please retry."
msgstr "下載失敗，請重試。"

#: error_dialogs.py:98
msgid ""
"<p>Please read the friendly <a href='{}'>manual</a> of how to install "
"pip.</p><p>If you still have this error, make sure you installed "
"calibre with the <a href='https://calibre-ebook.com/download_linux'>"
"binary install command</a> but not from Flathub or Snap Store.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>請閱讀如何安裝 pip 的<a href='{}'>說明文件</a>。</p>"
"<p>如果仍然遇到此錯誤，請確認是透過"
"<a href='https://calibre-ebook.com/download_linux'>二進位安裝指令</a>"
"而非從 Flathub 或 Snap Store 安裝 calibre。</p>"

#: error_dialogs.py:118
msgid "Please delete the '{}/worddumb-libs-py*' folder then try again."
msgstr "請刪除「{}/worddumb-libs-py*」資料夾後再試一次。"

#: error_dialogs.py:135
msgid ""
"<p>Read <a href='{}'>calibre FAQ</a> first then check your proxy "
"environment variables, they should be set by these commands:</p>"
"<p><code>$ export HTTP_PROXY='http://host:port'</code></p>"
"<p><code>$ export HTTPS_PROXY='http://host:port'</code></p>"
"<p>If you're allergic to terminal, close your proxy and use a VPN.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>請先閱讀 <a href='{}'>calibre FAQ</a>，然後檢查代理伺服器環境變數，"
"應透過以下指令設定：</p>"
"<p><code>$ export HTTP_PROXY='http://host:port'</code></p>"
"<p><code>$ export HTTPS_PROXY='http://host:port'</code></p>"
"<p>如果不想用終端機，請關閉代理伺服器並改用 VPN。</p>"

#: error_dialogs.py:148
msgid ""
"Is GitHub or Wikipedia blocked by your ISP? You might need to "
"bypass Internet censorship. Please read <a href='{}'>calibre FAQ</a>."
msgstr ""
"ISP 是否封鎖了 GitHub 或維基百科？可能需要繞過網路審查。"
"請閱讀 <a href='{}'>calibre FAQ</a>。"

#: error_dialogs.py:158
msgid ""
"An error occurred, please copy error message then report bug at "
"<a href=\"{}/issues\">GitHub</a>."
msgstr ""
"發生錯誤，請複製錯誤訊息後至 <a href=\"{}/issues\">GitHub</a> 回報問題。"

#: error_dialogs.py:175 error_dialogs.py:216
msgid "Unsupported language"
msgstr "不支援的語言"

#: error_dialogs.py:176
msgid "The language of the book <i>{}</i> is not supported."
msgstr "不支援書籍 <i>{}</i> 的語言。"

#: error_dialogs.py:181
msgid "Unsupported book format"
msgstr "不支援的書籍格式"

#: error_dialogs.py:181
msgid "The book format is not supported."
msgstr "不支援此書籍格式。"

#: error_dialogs.py:186
msgid "Device not found"
msgstr "找不到裝置"

#: error_dialogs.py:187
msgid "Definition data will be added when Kindle device is connected."
msgstr "連上 Kindle 裝置後，系統會自動加入釋義資料。"

#: error_dialogs.py:194
msgid "Word Wise database not found"
msgstr "找不到生詞提示資料庫"

#: error_dialogs.py:195
msgid ""
"Can't find Word Wise database on your device, open a Word Wise enabled "
"book to download this file."
msgstr ""
"在裝置上找不到生詞提示資料庫，請開啟已啟用生詞提示的書籍來下載此檔案。"

#: error_dialogs.py:205
msgid "Kindle doesn't support EPUB"
msgstr "Kindle 不支援 EPUB"

#: error_dialogs.py:206
msgid ""
"Kindle doesn't support EPUB format natively, please convert the book "
"format then try again."
msgstr "Kindle 原生不支援 EPUB 格式，請轉換書籍格式後再試一次。"

#: error_dialogs.py:217
msgid "Book language is not supported for the selected Word Wise gloss language."
msgstr "所選的生詞提示釋義語言不支援此書籍語言。"

#: error_dialogs.py:227
msgid ""
"Word Wise language must be set to Chinese on Kindle to display the "
"correct definitions when the \"Use Wiktionary definition\" option is "
"enabled."
msgstr ""
"啟用「使用維基詞典釋義」選項時，必須將 Kindle 上的生詞提示語言設為中文，"
"才能正確顯示釋義。"

